    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade BMW E46 M3, a pinnacle of analog driver engagement. This example is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine, featuring individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing for a razor-sharp throttle response. The power is delivered to the rear wheels via a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-calibrated M-Variable differential lock. Mechanically, this vehicle is impeccable; the critical rear subframe has been professionally reinforced, and the rod bearings have been replaced as a preventative measure. The suspension retains its factory-spec geometry with refreshed bushings and dampers, ensuring the chassis remains taut and communicative. The exterior finish is flawless, showing zero signs of track use or environmental wear. This is a turn-key acquisition for the purist seeking a mechanically synchronized, showroom-quality icon.",
